#. module: account_move_subscription
#: model:ir.actions.act_window,help:account_move_subscription.action_subscription_form
msgid ""
"A recurring entry occurs on a recurrent basis from a specific\n"
"                date, i.e. corresponding to the signature of a contract or an\n"
"                agreement with a customer or a supplier. You can create such\n"
"                entries to automate the postings in the system."
msgstr ""
"Una póliza recurrente se puede aplicar para las pólizas que se repiten mes a mes,\n"
"por ejemplo pólizas de amortización de gastos y/o inversiones,\n"
"nómina administrativa y/o cualquier otra posible afectación cada\n"
"cierre de mes."

